CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 17, 1956, pg. B11, reads: "'Bird Boys' of Pittsburgh getting their planes ready to wheel are, left to right, Jackie Butler, LuGene Bray, Milton Swan Jr., Sam Anderson and Leroy Randall Jr. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Leroy Randall Jr., Milton Swan Jr., and LuGene Bray, posed with radio-controlled model airplanes in K. Leroy Irvis' workshop, another version
